Details:
The labelled images under evaluation results seemed fine. I was able to evaluate the network and analyse video. A few markers were out of place so I wanted to refine that in refine trackets. So I converted into tracklets which was again successful, but when I uploaded the files,I got the error mentioned in title. 

Steps to reproduce the behavior:
1. Go to 'Refine tracklets'
2. Click on 'Launch GUI' after uploading video and shuffle-50000bx file
3. See error "OS error: Tracklets are empty" in terminal


**Additional context**
I am not sure if it has something to do with this:
rpck nan rpck train: nan
rmse nan miss nan hit nan

Thank you for your help!
